QuestData.Title: Fungal Bundle
QuestData.Description: The umbraspore giant you killed seemed immune to the volatile spores in the area. Perhaps the odd growths you found all over its body contribute to its immunity. You grab a big, disgusting fungal lump in order to give it to the rangari for study.
QuestData.LogDescription: Take the Curious Growth to Rangari Sheera at the Rangari Enclave in Shadowmoon Valley.
